rComments: I absolutely loved Prof. Silverman. She's very clear on what she expects of her students. Be in class, read the lectures, incorporate those two in your papers and you're set. Would definitely take again!

If you can, absolutely take a course with this professor. She is so smart and kind and makes the lectures beyond interesting. Does case studies in the course, and it is easy to understand the subject matter. The assignments are easy and as long as you try, you can do really well in this course. Take a course with her, you won't regret it!

Marjorie est une professeure qui est toujours bien préparée et connaît très bien sa matière. Son cours ressemble beaucoup à Diversité en service social. Ses cours étaient très intéressants et donnaient une perspective différente sur le vécu des personnes âgées. J'ai beaucoup apprécié son cours. Facile et enrichissant, je le recommande.
Bonne prof. Son cours est facile. Tu peut avoir une très bonne note si tu ecrit beaucoup dans ses exams

pretty easy class, explains what she expects from you for exams and projects. she lets students chose whether they want to do a midterm or volunteer work instead. If you chose the volunteer work, you can automatically get an extra 5% on your grade if you explain to the class in a two-minute presentation. Pretty easy grader and interesting subject
